  "title": "Business Development Specialist (Digital Resource Solutions) #80051",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Digital Resources Solutions Provider</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Business Development Specialist</strong></li><li>Working Location: Kaki Bukit</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days, Monday – Friday (9am – 6pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Reach out to and build connections with prospects in libraries, corporate sectors, universities and research institutions.</li><li>Present our advanced digital research tools via email outreach, phone conversations, and online meetings.</li><li>Deliver interactive demonstrations that highlight the value and functionality of our technology solutions.</li><li>Work closely with the Marketing team to develop persuasive proposals and impactful presentations.</li><li>Monitor market developments to identify fresh opportunities for expansion and innovation.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma holder is preferred.</li><li>Self-driven individuals with a strong desire to grow and acquire new knowledge.</li><li>Excellent interpersonal and communication abilities.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80051 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
